headline: Saudi Construction Equipment Market to Surge: Can CAT Capitalize?
summary: Caterpillar is set to benefit as Saudi Arabia's equipment market is expected to grow 5.92% over 2024-2030, fueled by Vision 2030 infrastructure goals.
